'I see that you have gained proficiency as an expert cook! That is excellent, [placeholder]. You are showing remarkable progress.

'You are about ready to learn to be an artisan cook, which is the next step along your path to mastery. To do this, though, you will need to prove your worth to me.

'If you impress me, I may allow you to use the superior oven to create delectable foods from your artisan recipes. Not many have this honour!'

'I haven't eaten in a full two hours! My friends were supposed to sup with me, but they keep insisting that I find them first. They are hiding, and they seem to be quite content where they are.\n\n'Thank you most kindly for this small meal! I was close to collapsing from hunger.'

'Oh, yum! Yum-yum-yum. I needed this delivery because I ate my wife's pie filling, you see. I needed to replace it quickly. I hope she doesn't notice.\n\n'That really does smell most remarkable. May...may I have a taste?'

'I have a hungry patron who ordered a beef stew, but I'm all out! Thank you so much for delivering this, [placeholder]. I hear you are a very skilled cook...well on your way to surpassing expert level, even!'
Jewel Underhill is next to the superior oven in Michel Delving.\n\nYou should complete Jewel Underhill's cooking task.
